5a7f80><div class="blog-card__wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><div class="blog-card__image-wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><a href="/all-resources/automation-isnt-the-hard-part-anymore" class="" aria-label="Read more about {{ story.content.title }}" data-v-415a7f80><img onerror="this.setAttribute(&#39;data-error&#39;, 1)" width="400" height="400" alt="Automation Isn’t the Hard Part Anymore" data-nuxt-img srcset="/storyblok/f/337048/1638x1076/1ce8aa1225/truck.png 1x, /storyblok/f/337048/1638x1076/1ce8aa1225/truck.png 2x" class="blog-card__image" src="/storyblok/f/337048/1638x1076/1ce8aa1225/truck.png" data-v-415a7f80><button class="blog-card__button button label-4 blog-card__button" style="--hover-bg:rgba(5, 36, 36, 1);--hover-color:rgba(171, 255, 2, 1);--base-color:white;" data-v-415a7f80 data-v-d8fa3fef><span class="link-active" data-v-d8fa3fef><!--[-->Read More<!--]--></span></button></a></div><div class="blog-card__content" data-v-415a7f80><p class="blog-card__category" data-v-415a7f80>blog</p><a href="/all-resources/automation-isnt-the-hard-part-anymore" class="" aria-label="Read more about {{ story.content.title }}" data-v-415a7f80><h3 class="blog-card__title" data-v-415a7f80>Automation Isn’t the Hard Part Anymore</h3></a><p class="blog-card__excerpt" data-v-415a7f80>For years, supply chain innovation has been defined by a race toward automation. Companies invested heavily in robotics, sensors, AI tools, autonomous equipment, and warehouse modernization initiatives, all with the promise of faster operations and greater efficiency.</p><!----></div></div></div><div class="blog-card category-resources__item" data-v-ff2e5701 data-v-415a7f80><div class="blog-card__wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><div class="blog-card__image-wrapper" data-v-415a7f80><a href="/all-resources/amazon-just-turned-its-supply-chain-into-a-product-here-s-what-that-means-for-the-yard" class="" aria-label="Read more about {{ story.content.title }}" data-v-415a7f80><img onerror="this.setAttribute(&#39;data-error&#3